{"tid":1562836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搲撚曬頭，消防可唔可以計返啱條數比大家睇？","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:40:41.000Z","uid":159485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8612aaf36b1efd9d5c67cfaf6857a76ac45f7e","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFyKTYv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFyKTYv.png&h=a4c63305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身<br />\n0015: 10 人傷（當中 6 嚴重）<br />\n0102: 7 人傷（當中 3 嚴重）<br />\n<br />\n啱啱記者會 Madam 話因為嚴重可以本身氣促變到唔氣促，所以嚴重變返唔嚴重，但<span style=\"color: red;\">按理佢地都照係歸類為受傷（非紅色），咁點解 0102 時總受傷人數會變返做 7 人</span>？<br />\n<br />\n而如果係按照佢另一種講法，就係嚴重人數方面係有重覆點算情況，咁會衍生另外兩個問題<br />\n1. 得三個人，你又話係同一個救護人員做點算，點解可以<span style=\"color: red;\">得三個人都認唔到而 100% 重覆點算</span>？<br />\n2. 如果真係有重覆點算，咁你又話佢地係好轉。咁<span style=\"color: red;\">入面有幾多個人係重覆點算咗，有幾多個係好轉咗</span>？數字上點解釋到，總人數跌、但同時嚴重人數又跌？咁究竟佢地係真係有好轉，定你地係估佢地有好轉？ <br />\n<br />\n去到啱啱記者問，究竟係「情況好轉」定「重覆點算」，Madam 終於承認<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔知」、「我都想知」</span>，淨係不斷話，因為最先果個救護人員落到去唔記得帶張濕鳩分類咭，所以就唔肯定。<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬，<span style=\"color: red;\">三個嚴重咋，而家叫你記圓周率咩</span>。三個人傷勢、病情冇可能一樣，你評估病人嘅時候，會同佢對話、睇佢病情、再按佢病徵分類佢嚴重情況，如果好似你講咁，係同一個人去做，有乜可能 100% 重覆？<br />\n<br />\n一定要解釋，係「情況好轉」定「重覆點算」，同埋人數方面點解咁撚棘！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">否則，831 三個嚴重嘅患者，到而家都係失蹤！</span>"},{"pid":"df08cc254fa3a51f9c9e86748bbebabec75041f8","tid":1562836,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c740476756b8e43498115c7c168fe9889374e74e","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"d131c9a702236814cad381b35bbc012a79c2f9b1","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"8b4a7aeab74e92e8a0d1733aaad12589a911c744","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"53eaacfaf5a42eaf2bf8f9dba8fffb33a5637578","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"4a04872f70d7bb7e5c62975fed69b9735d72f9df","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"ae64faa713a085605c91455575a01b4c1c5c5948","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"6cb4fc474b48ea6a80c133b984c4cff12e39373e","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"6d50923d14a6ef88491dde9c0d1fa14f5329061a","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"3678ebc3d065e6383be8cc30075d87f3df331d0c","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"c3690aa11102010c3e06d3298678b46035fa178e","tid":1562836,"uid":159485,"like":0,"